name: CD - ONE 'World in Decay' EP 5 track
description:
Get ONE's debut EP sent directly to you for your hi-fi listening pleasure!

The hard hitting and sonically diverse debut EP is just the beginning for ONE. The contrasting dynamic of the Melbourne based 5 piece ranges from down-tuned chug-guitar with screamed vocals to subtle lyrical moments with layered atmospheric instrumentation.

1. No Compromise
2. Can I
3. World of Decay
4. White Red Black
5. Faith

Released 11 November 2011
Produced by ONE & Mat Robins

Recorded & mixed at ColourSound Studios by Mat Robins
www.coloursoundstudio.com

Mastered at Woodstock Studios by Cam Trewin

If you would prefer a digital download of the EP, head here:
www.onesounds.bandcamp.com
